errata 2: turns out there is no caps in an eq log in.   again eww very bad.  i kept trying my station log in with the caps i use in the eq login kept coming back as invalid. that was a hmmm. but then i played a hunch and tried my password without caps.  it went. so then i played another hunch and went into eq and tried my password without caps: it went.  conclusion: eq changes passwords to all lowercase before submitting station doesnt.   thats just gross =/  so ignore advice about uppercases they dont apply here.  oddly dont apply here...<br>
