errate 4: all of these changes the basic conclusion.  eq accounts are very hackable if you a)make your username known via posting using it and b) have a vulnerable password.  <br>
<br>
this is real ya all. the existance of a httplogin attempt, a web based login attempt, makes any password system unsafe if the password is weak. reference passport discussions. it allows literally a 1000+ of changes of identity in the attempt. it also opens it up to non-eq specific programs .  in lightof that also taking steps to hide your username is good. you dont have to post with it right? i dunno.<br>
